title: Civil War in the Cumberland Plateau Event (NPS - National Park Service)
text: ( Source : NPS - National Park Service ) Date : October 13 , 2015 Contact : Joe Zagorski Contact: Christopher Derman The Obed Wild and Scenic River announces a Civil War lecture and book signing on Saturday, November 7 , beginning at 1 p.m. (ET).
